<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
    <title>Offline</title>
    <link
      data-testid="unpkg-link"
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://unpkg.com/@mcgill-wsg/mcgill-ds@1/dist/css/mds.css"
    />
    <style type="text/css">
      header,
      footer {
        padding: var(--mds-spacing-medium);
      }

      header {
        padding-top: 0;
        padding-bottom: 0;
        box-shadow: var(--mds-shadow-small);
      }

      .page-bottom {
        /*  In flex column, this moves to this element to bottom.  */
        margin-top: auto;
      }

      .page-bottom .footer-top {
        background: var(--mds-color-gray-900);
      }

      footer .copyright {
        margin-left: auto;
      }

      .banner-logo {
        background: var(--mds-color-primary-500);
        padding: var(--mds-spacing-small);
        /*  To accomodate overhang style.  */
        margin-bottom: -5px;
        box-shadow: var(--mds-shadow-small);
      }

      .w-80 {
        max-width: 80vw;
      }

      .full-height {
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      /* Unset grid; revert to block display on mobile. */
      @media (max-width: 320px) {
        div[class*="mds-l-grid"] {
          display: block;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="mds-l-flex full-height">
      <header class="mds-header">
        <div class="mds-mx--center w-80">
          <a title="McGill University" href="https://www.mcgill.ca/">
            <img
              alt="McGill University logo"
              class="banner-logo mds-logo--md"
              src="https://unpkg.com/@mcgill-wsg/mcgill-ds@1.0.40/dist/assets/svgs/logo--inverted.svg"
            />
          </a>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="mds-mx--center mds-mt--large w-80">
        <div class="mds-l-grid--desktop-2 mds-l-gap--3">
          <section>
            <h2 class="mds-my--large">Can't load page</h2>
            <p>
              This is temporary. Wait a moment and then try reloading the page. It may
              help to:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>
                Clear your browser cache or use an incognito (private) browsing mode.
              </li>
              <li>
               Off-campus McGill users: please ensure you're connected to the McGill VPN.
              </li>
              <li>
                Ensure JavaScript is enabled in your browser.
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              Still not working? <a href="https://mcgill.service-now.com/itportal?id=sc_cat_item&sys_id=67f6bdfadbe5d494ed7c8043059619fb&sysparm_category=b03f88914f4a9200b18f59dd0210c784">Submit an incident report</a>. Be sure to include:
            </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Type of error: <strong>Content blocked by network security rules</strong></li>
                <li>Your support ID is <strong id="support-id-en">BOT-17147304893834573355</strong></li>
              </ul>
            <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>

          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="mds-my--large">La page ne se charge pas</h2>
            <p>
              C'est temporaire. Attendez un peu, puis essayez de la recharger. Quelques conseils :
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Videz la mémoire cache de votre navigateur ou utilisez un mode de navigation privée.</li>
              <li>Utilisateurs de McGill hors campus : veuillez vous assurer que vous êtes connectés au VPN de McGill.</li>
              <li>Assurez-vous que JavaScript est activé dans votre navigateur.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              Ça ne fonctionne toujours pas? <a href="https://mcgill.service-now.com/itportal?id=sc_cat_item&sys_id=67f6bdfadbe5d494ed7c8043059619fb&sysparm_category=b03f88914f4a9200b18f59dd0210c784">Présentez un rapport d'incident</a> comprenant l'information suivante :

            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>le type d'erreur : <strong>Content blocked by network security rules;</strong></li>
              <li>le numéro d'identification du support : <strong id="support-id-fr"></strong>.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              Nous vous remercions de votre patience.
            </p>
          </section>

        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="page-bottom">
        <div
          class="footer-top mds-dark mds-mt--large"
        >
          <div class="mds-mx--center w-80">
            <div class="mds-l-grid--cols-2 mds-l-gap--3">
              <div class="mds-my--large mds-copy--micro">
                <p>For on-campus emergencies</p>
                <tel>514-398-3000</tel> <span>(downtown campus)</span>
                <br />
                <tel>514-398-7777</tel> <span>(Macdonald campus)</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mds-my--large mds-copy--micro">
                <p>En cas d'urgence</p>

                <tel>514-398-3000</tel> <span>(campus centre-ville)</span>
                <br />
                <tel>514-398-7777</tel> <span>(campus Macdonald)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <footer class="mds-footer mds-dark">
          <div
            class="
              mds-mx--center
              w-80
              mds-l-flex-row
              mds-l-justify--start
              mds-l-align--center
            "
          >
            <a title="McGill University" href="https://www.mcgill.ca/">
              <img
                alt="McGill University logo"
                class="mds-logo--sm"
                src="https://unpkg.com/@mcgill-wsg/mcgill-ds@1.0.40/dist/assets/svgs/logo--inverted.svg"
              />
            </a>

            <div class="copyright">
              <span class="mds-copy--muted mds-copy--micro"
                >© McGill University / Université McGill</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </footer>
      </section>
    </div>

  <script>
    // Copy the support ID from English section to French section
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      const enSupportId = document.getElementById('support-id-en');
      const frSupportId = document.getElementById('support-id-fr');
      if (enSupportId && frSupportId) {
        frSupportId.textContent = enSupportId.textContent;
      }
    });
  </script>
  </body>
</html>